    "faq_qH4CGn": {
      "type": "faq",
      "blocks": {
        "question_9PeHqA": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "1. What is a folding electric bike?",
            "title_tag": "h3",
            "text": "<p>A folding electric bike is an ebike designed with a collapsible frame, making it easy to store, transport, and ride. Folding electric bikes combine portability with electric assist, perfect for commuting and everyday travel.</p>",
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        },
        "question_GXQf8j": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "2. Are foldable electric bikes good for adults?",
            "title_tag": "h3",
            "text": "<p>Yes. Foldable electric bikes for adults offer a comfortable ride with the added benefit of compact storage. They’re ideal for commuters, travelers, and riders who need a space-saving ebike.</p>",
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        },
        "question_VFgaGh": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "3. How small does a folding ebike get when folded?",
            "title_tag": "h3",
            "text": "<p>Most folding ebikes fold down to a compact footprint that fits more easily in apartments, garages, or vehicle storage. For example, the Jasion Hunter Pro has been cited as folding down to about 39.8″ × 25.6″ × 31.5″, which makes it trunk/RV-friendly for many riders. If you want a portable setup for road trips, compare the folded size and how easy the folding steps feel for you.</p>",
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        },
        "question_63FcMh": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "4. Can I fit a folding electric bike in a car trunk or RV?",
            "title_tag": "h3",
            "text": "<p>Yes. One of the biggest benefits of a foldable electric bike is that it can be stored in a car trunk, RV, or camper, making it a great choice for road trips and travel adventures.</p>",
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        },
        "question_iCdAHg": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "5. Are folding ebikes good for commuting?",
            "title_tag": "h3",
            "text": "<p>Yes—folding ebikes are great for commuting because they’re easy to park and store at home or the office, and they work well for mixed trips (drive + ride, train + ride). For everyday urban commuting, a balanced folding ebike is often the most convenient option.</p>",
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        },
        "question_PGE7BB": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "6. How much does a lightweight folding ebike weigh?",
            "title_tag": "h3",
            "text": "<p>A lightweight folding ebike typically weighs between 50–70 lbs depending on the battery and motor size. Jasion designs folding ebikes to balance portability with power for adults.</p>",
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        },
        "question_wFc33i": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "7. How far can a folding ebike go on a single charge?",
            "title_tag": "h3",
            "text": "<p>Most folding ebikes can travel 30–60 miles per charge depending on rider weight, terrain, and assist level. Jasion folding electric bikes feature efficient batteries for daily commuting range.</p>",
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        },
        "question_xaF7fE": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "8. How do I choose the best folding electric bike?",
            "title_tag": "h3",
            "text": "<p>To choose the best folding electric bike, consider your commute distance, storage needs, motor power, and comfort. Foldable electric bikes are best when they match your lifestyle and travel habits.</p>",
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        },
        "question_9mGdcT": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "9. Are folding ebikes easy to fold and carry?",
            "title_tag": "h3",
            "text": "<p>Yes. We design our folding ebikes with a straightforward folding process so riders can store or transport the bike without hassle. Folding is especially convenient for small-space storage, mixed commuting (drive + ride), and travel. <br/>Which Jasion folding ebike should </p>",
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        },
        "question_6P74Wq": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "10. Which Jasion folding ebike should I pick: Hunter Pro, X-Hunter, or X-Hunter ST?",
            "title_tag": "h3",
            "text": "<p>Here’s a simple way to choose:<br/>● <a href=\"https://www.jasionbike.com/products/hunter-pro\" title=\"https://www.jasionbike.com/products/hunter-pro\">Hunter Pro</a>: a strong all-around folding ebike for daily riding and value.<br/>●<a href=\"https://www.jasionbike.com/products/jasion-x-hunter\" title=\"https://www.jasionbike.com/products/jasion-x-hunter\"> X-Hunter</a>: built for all-terrain use with 85 Nm torque, a great pick if you want more climbing power.<br/>● <a href=\"https://www.jasionbike.com/products/x-hunter-st\" title=\"https://www.jasionbike.com/products/x-hunter-st\">X-Hunter ST:</a> a higher-output option labeled 1400W, ideal if you want extra performance for tougher routes.</p>",
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        }
